        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Fred Korematsu Congressional Gold Medal Act of 2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill provides for the award of a Congressional Gold Medal posthumously to Fred Korematsu in recognition of his contributions to civil rights, his loyalty and patriotism to the nation, and his dedication to justice and equality.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
